skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: pushing midnight
des: The Pushing Midnight skill allows you to find out about the band Pushing Midnight, a rock/pop cover band based out of Woodinville, WA. You can hear about a randomly selected event on their upcoming calendar by saying 'Alexa, ask Pushing Midnight whats coming up' or you can find out which show is next by saying 'Alexa, ask Pushing Midnight when is the next show' to hear a description of the event.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
